\c 2
\s UDavida ubekwa abe yinkosi yakoJuda
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi emva kwalokho uDavida wabuza eN\nd kosi\nd*ni esithi: Ngenyukele yini komunye wemizi yakoJuda\x + Nani 27.21.\x*? IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuye: Yenyuka. UDavida wasesithi: Ngiye ngaphi? Yasisithi: EHebroni\x + Josh. 10.3.\x*.
\v 2 Ngakho uDavida wenyukela lapho, kanye labafazi bakhe bobabili, uAhinowama umJizereyelikazi loAbigayili umkaNabali umKharmeli\x + 1 Sam. 25.43.\x*.
\v 3 UDavida wasesenyusa abantu bakhe ababelaye, ngulowo lalowo labendlu yakhe; basebehlala emizini yeHebroni\x + 1 Sam. 27.2,3. 30.1. 1 Lan. 12.1.\x*.
\v 4 Kwasekufika abantu bakoJuda, bamgcoba khona uDavida waba yinkosi phezu kwendlu yakoJuda\x + 2.11. 5.5.\x*. Basebemtshela uDavida besithi: Abantu beJabeshi-Gileyadi yibo abangcwaba uSawuli\x + 1 Sam. 31.13. Hlu. 21.8.\x*.
\p
\v 5 UDavida wasethumela izithunywa ebantwini beJabeshi-Gileyadi\x + 1 Sam. 31.13. Hlu. 21.8.\x*, wathi kibo: Kalibusiswe yiN\nd kosi\nd*, ngoba lenze lumusa enkosini yenu, kuSawuli, lamngcwaba\x + Ruthe 2.20.\x*.
\v 6 Khathesi-ke, iN\nd kosi\nd* kayilenzele umusa leqiniso; mina lami ngizalenzela lokhu okuhle, ngoba lenze loludaba\x + 2 Tim. 1.16,18.\x*.
\v 7 Khathesi-ke kaziqine izandla zenu libe ngamadodana amaqhawe; ngoba inkosi yenu uSawuli ifile; njalo lendlu yakoJuda ingigcobile mina ukuba yinkosi phezu kwabo.
\s UDavida ulwa labendlu kaSawuli
\p
\v 8 Kodwa uAbhineri indodana kaNeri\x + 3.6. 1 Sam. 14.50. 17.55. 20.25. 26.5,7,14,15. 1 Kho. 2.5. 1 Lan. 26.28.\x*, induna yebutho uSawuli ayelalo, wathatha uIshiboshethi indodana kaSawuli, wamchaphisela eMahanayimi\x + 17.24.\x*,
\v 9 wambeka waba yinkosi phezu kweGileyadi\x + 1 Lan. 12.29,30,36,37.\x*, laphezu kwamaAshuri\x + 1 Lan. 12.29,30,36,37.\x*, laphezu kweJizereyeli\x + Josh. 17.16.\x*, laphezu kukaEfrayimi\x + 1 Lan. 12.29,30,36,37.\x*, laphezu kukaBhenjamini\x + 1 Lan. 12.29,30,36,37.\x*, laphezu kukaIsrayeli wonke.
\v 10 UIshiboshethi, indodana kaSawuli, wayeleminyaka engamatshumi amane esiba yinkosi phezu kukaIsrayeli, wabusa iminyaka emibili. Kodwa indlu yakoJuda yalandela uDavida.
\v 11 Lenani lensuku uDavida owaba yinkosi ngazo eHebroni phezu kwendlu yakoJuda laliyiminyaka eyisikhombisa lenyanga eziyisithupha\x + Josh. 10.3.\x*.
\p
\v 12 UAbhineri indodana kaNeri wasephuma, lenceku zikaIshiboshethi indodana kaSawuli, basuka eMahanayimi baya eGibeyoni\x + Josh. 9.3.\x*.
\v 13 UJowabi indodana kaZeruya lenceku zikaDavida basebephuma bahlangana ndawonye echibini leGibeyoni\x + Jer. 41.12.\x*; bahlala, abanye ngapha kwechibi labanye ngale kwechibi.
\v 14 UAbhineri wasesithi kuJowabi: Amajaha ake asukume adlale phambi kwethu. UJowabi wasesithi: Kawasukume.
\v 15 Kwasekusukuma kwedlula ngenani abalitshumi lambili koBhenjamini lakoIshiboshethi indodana kaSawuli, letshumi lambili lenceku zikaDavida.
\v 16 Basebebamba ngulowo lalowo ikhanda lomunye, \add wagwaza\add* \add nge\add*nkemba yakhe ehlangothini lomunye; ngokunjalo bawa ndawonye. Ngakho leyondawo bayibiza \add ngokuthi\add* yiHelekati-Hasurimi eseGibeyoni.
\v 17 Njalo kwaba lempi enzima kakhulu ngalolosuku, loAbhineri wehlulwa lamadoda akoIsrayeli phambi kwenceku zikaDavida.
\p
\v 18 Ayekhona-ke lapho amadodana amathathu kaZeruya, oJowabi, loAbishayi loAsaheli\x + 1 Sam. 26.6.\x*. Njalo uAsaheli wayelesiqubu ezinyaweni\x + Amos 2.15.\x* njengomunye wemiziki yeganga\x + 22.34. 1 Lan. 12.8. Hlab. 18.33.\x*.
\v 19 UAsaheli wasexotshana loAbhineri; njalo ekuhambeni kwakhe kaphambukelanga ngakwesokunene langakwesokhohlo ekulandeleni uAbhineri.
\v 20 UAbhineri wasenyemukula, wathi: Nguwe uAsaheli yini? Wasesithi: Yimi.
\v 21 UAbhineri wasesithi kuye: Phambukela wena ngakwesokunene loba ngakwesokhohlo, uzibambele elinye lamajaha, uzithathele izikhali zalo. Kodwa uAsaheli kavumanga ukuphambuka ekumlandeleni.
\v 22 UAbhineri wasebuya futhi esithi kuAsaheli: Phambuka wena ekungilandeleni; ngizakutshayelelani emhlabathini? Pho, ngingaphakamisa njani ubuso bami kuJowabi umfowenu\x + 1 Sam. 19.17.\x*?
\v 23 Kodwa wala ukuphambuka; ngakho uAbhineri wamtshaya ngesidindi somkhonto kubambo lwesihlanu, umkhonto waze waphuma emuva kwakhe; wasewela phansi lapho, wafela kuleyondawo. Kwasekusithi bonke abafika endaweni lapho uAsaheli awela wafa khona, bema\x + 3.27. 4.6. 20.10.\x*.
\v 24 UJowabi laye loAbishayi baxotshana loAbhineri; ilanga laselitshona, bona befika eqaqeni lweAma, olungaphambi kweGiya endleleni yenkangala yeGibeyoni.
\p
\v 25 Abantwana bakoBhenjamini basebebuthana ngemva kukaAbhineri, baba lixuku linye, bema phezu koqaqa oluthile.
\v 26 UAbhineri wasememeza kuJowabi wathi: Inkemba izakudla njalonjalo yini? Kawazi yini ukuthi kuzakuba yikubaba ekucineni? Koze kube nini ungabatsheli abantu ukuthi babuye ekulandeleni abafowabo?
\v 27 UJowabi wasesithi: Kuphila kukaNkulunkulu, ngaphandle kokuthi ubukhulumile, isibili ngalesosikhathi kusukela ekuseni abantu ngabe benyukile, ngulowo lalowo esuka ekulandeleni umfowabo\x + 2.14. Zaga 17.14.\x*.
\v 28 UJowabi wasevuthela uphondo, bonke abantu basebesima, kababe besaxotshana loIsrayeli, futhi kababe besalwa njalo.
\v 29 UAbhineri labantu bakhe bahamba bedabula amagceke bonke lobobusuku, bachapha iJordani, badabula iBhithironi yonke, bafika eMahanayimi\x + 17.24.\x*.
\v 30 UJowabi wasebuya ekulandeleni uAbhineri; esebuthanisile bonke abantu, encekwini zikaDavida kwasilela abalitshumi labayisificamunwemunye, loAsaheli.
\v 31 Kodwa izinceku zikaDavida zazitshayile koBhenjamini lemadodeni akaAbhineri; amadoda angamakhulu amathathu lamatshumi ayisithupha afa.
\p
\v 32 Basebemthatha uAsaheli, bamngcwaba engcwabeni likayise elaliseBhethelehema. UJowabi labantu bakhe basebehamba ubusuku bonke, kwasa beseHebroni\x + 2.18. 3.22. 8.16. 11.1. 12.26. 14.1. 18.2,10. 19.1. 20.7,23. 24.2,3. 1 Sam. 26.6. 1 Kho. 1.7. 2.5,28. 11.15. 1 Lan. 2.16. 26.28. 27.24,34.\x*.
